        <gcds-heading tag="h2" id="overview">Overview</gcds-heading>
        <gcds-text>
            This page documents all available utility classes in the GC Foundation system. These classes are based on the 
            <gcds-link href="https://design-system.alpha.canada.ca/en/styles/spacing/">GCDS design system spacing</gcds-link> 
            and provide a consistent way to apply styling throughout your application.
        </gcds-text>

        <hr />

        <gcds-heading tag="h2" id="spacing" margin-bottom="300">Spacing Scale</gcds-heading>
