            </gcds-text>
            
        <div class="fdcp-bg-gray-50 fdcp-p-300">
            <code>0, 25, 50, 75, 100, 125, 150, 175, 200, 225, 250, 300, 350, 400, 450, 500, 550, 600, 650, 700, 750, 800, 850, 900, 950, 1000</code>
        </div>

        <hr />

        <gcds-heading tag="h2" id="best-practices" margin-bottom="300">Best Practices</gcds-heading>
        <gcds-grid columns="repeat(2, 1fr)" gap="1rem">
            <div>
                <gcds-heading tag="h3" margin-bottom="200">✅ Do:</gcds-heading>
                <ul>
                    <li>Use consistent spacing tokens from the design system</li>
                    <li>Prefer utility classes for spacing over custom CSS</li>
                    <li>Use responsive utilities to optimize mobile experience</li>
                    <li>Combine utilities for complex layouts</li>
                    <li>Use semantic color classes (primary, secondary, danger)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <gcds-heading tag="h3" margin-bottom="200">❌ Don't:</gcds-heading>
                <ul>
                    <li>Create custom spacing values outside the scale</li>
                    <li>Use magic numbers for spacing</li>
                    <li>Override utility classes with custom CSS</li>
                    <li>Use too many utility classes that make HTML unreadable</li>
                    <li>Forget to test responsive behavior</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </gcds-grid>
    </div>
